
1) build your repository first and git clone to the local folder.

$ git clone ....git

directly initialize the local git

2) 初始化git

$ git config --global user.name "<用户名>"
$ git config --global user.email "<电子邮件>"

以下命令能让Git以彩色显示。

$ git config --global color.ui auto

您可以为Git命令设定别名。例如：把「checkout」缩略为「co」，然后就使用「co」来执行命令。

$ git config --global alias.co checkout

3）建立本地git数据库

首先在任意一个地方创建tutorial目录。然后使用init命令把该tutorial目录移动到本地Git数据库。

$ git init

按照以下步骤把新创建的tutorial目录设置到Git数据库。

4）使用status命令确认工作树和索引的状态。

$ git status

5) how to add files

 git add file
 git commit -m "Adding files"
 git status
 git push origin master

6) how to delete files

  git rm file
  git commit -m "Deleting files"
  git status
  git push origin master

  to delete and add together
	
  git add file1
  git rm file2
  git commit -m "deleting and adding files"
  git push origin master

7) how to delete a branch

Manually enter the URL for your repository's Settings page in your browser:
	https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/YOUR-REPOSITORY/settings
Repository deletion buttonUnder Danger Zone, click Delete this reposit

8) how to add a git repository

9) git pull origin master

10) git push

11) git status

git add .

12) let you git know the remote git so you can push your files to

	git remote add origin htt0://github.ericwang915.git
 	when you do "git clone", the original file is already there.

13) if the file is totally a new file

make your current folder as a git:
	git init

see the status of the git:

	git status

add the file to the git:

	git add  1.jpg

commit the file:

	git commit -m "add the file"

let the created git know the main git

	git remote add origin http://

	git remote -v

push your file:

	git push origin master

14) generate a new branch

	git branch newbranch
	git checkout newbranch
	git merge master
        git push origin master
	git push origin newbranch
	git diff newbranch master
	git fetch origin
	git pull origin master --allow-unrelated-histories
15) delete a branch
	git branch -d (-D) newbranch
	git push origin :newbranch

16) change the remote name:
	git remote rm origin
	git remote rename origin destination










